data.title: Gardening is my source of contentment

images.description:
Getting my hands dirty in the soil and feeding the flowers with water grounds me. Gardening is a source of my satisfaction. It connects me every day with the cycles of life on our earth: germinating, reaping and passing away - all stages are part of a cycle, and it fills my heart with joy and gratitude to consciously experience this process.
